===Etymology 1===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*gʷʰedʰ-}}
From {{der|en|enm|bidden}}, from the {{der|en|ang|-}} verb {{m|ang|biddan||ask, demand}}, from {{der|en|gem-pro|*bidjaną||to ask}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*gʷʰedʰ-}}. Conflated with the {{der|en|ang|-}} verb {{m|ang|bēodan||offer, announce}} (see Etymology 2 below). Compare {{cog|fy|bidde}}, {{cog|nds|bidden}}, {{cog|nl|bidden}} ("to pray"), {{cog|de|bitten}}, {{cog|da|bede}}, {{cog|nb|be}}.

